                            	    41: *
00:0001091A 60000022        	    42: START	BRA	CSTART		Cold Start entry point
00:0001091E 60000052        	    43: GOWARM	BRA	WSTART		Warm Start entry point
00:00010922 60000D3E        	    44: GOOUT	BRA	OUTC		Jump to character-out routine
