00:0001092A 60000D4C        	    46: GOAUXO	BRA	AUXOUT		Jump to auxiliary-out routine
00:0001092E 60000D58        	    47: GOAUXI	BRA	AUXIN		Jump to auxiliary-in routine
00:00010932 60000D5A        	    48: GOBYE	BRA	BYEBYE		Jump to monitor, DOS, etc.
